    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the heads up. i checked and there isn't anything sticking in the fan blades, they spin fine if i poke them with a stick. the humming just keeps happening when the unit tries to kick on. could it be a part that's gone bad like a capacitor or something? i'm kinda worried about that electrical noise.",
